query:
SELECT 
    v.id as venda_id,
    v.formandoId,
    v.excluido,
    v.excluidoEm,
    f.id as formando_id_real,
    f.turmaId,
    t.codigo as turma_codigo,
    DATE_FORMAT(v.dataVenda, '%d/%m/%Y %H:%i:%s') as data_venda
FROM vendas v 
LEFT JOIN formandos f ON v.formandoId = f.id
LEFT JOIN turmas t ON f.turmaId = t.id
WHERE v.dataVenda BETWEEN '2026-06-14 00:00:00' AND '2026-06-15 23:59:59'
ORDER BY v.excluido, v.id
